{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Zuh\u00f6rerinnen und Zuh\u00f6rer! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachdem nun ein Professor geredet hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.640", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "redet jetzt ein Bergmann zu Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Kind des Ruhrgebiets."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kampf gegen die Langzeitarbeitslosigkeit bleibt f\u00fcr uns Arbeitsmarktpolitiker wohl die schwerste Aufgabe \u00fcberhaupt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.360", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was hilft Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Weg raus aus dem ALG-Il-Bezug zu finden? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.240", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Ma\u00dfnahmen bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sanktionen verschlimmern ihre Lebenssituation wom\u00f6glich?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Abgeordneter des Reviers, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo Arbeitslosigkeit ein sichtbares Problem ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kenne ich das eine oder andere Schicksal sehr genau. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gang zum Jobcenter ist keinesfalls leicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.360", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So manche Sanktion verschlimmert die pers\u00f6nliche Situation und wird als vorschnell oder gar respektlos empfunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.640", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch tue ich mich schwer mit der generellen Abschaffung von Sanktionen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind Art und Umfang von Sanktionen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.280", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sollten meiner Meinung nach abgemildert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum geht es unterm Strich? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.320", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist das Signal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass jede und jeder Betroffene auch einen Teil zur Verbesserung der eigenen Situation beitragen muss und sich nicht ausnahmslos auf die Solidargemeinschaft verl\u00e4sst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um Rechte und um Pflichten sowie um das eigene Bem\u00fchen und nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erwerbslose unter Generalverdacht zu stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.080", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es uns die Fraktion Die Linke in ihrem Antrag unterstellt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.440", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir hatten in der vergangenen Wahlperiode eine sehr ausf\u00fchrliche Anh\u00f6rung zum Thema \u201eSanktionen bei Hartz\u00a0IV\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.600", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei gab es gute Argumente f\u00fcr die Beibehaltung von Sanktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch f\u00fcr ihre Abschaffung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.760", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die SPD-Fraktion h\u00e4tte gerne bei den Regelungen f\u00fcr unter 25-J\u00e4hrige gehandelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sch\u00e4rfere Sanktionen f\u00fcr junge Erwerbslose sind nicht hinnehmbar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.760", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Sanktionierung von Leistungen f\u00fcr Kosten der Unterkunft lehnen wir ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.800", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen keine Existenzen vernichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern Chancen geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.720", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist Diplomatie gefragt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schlie\u00dflich ist die Lebenslage aus Sicht der Leistungsbezieher schlimm genug: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.840", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst ist der Job weg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann wird das Geld weniger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der soziale Status br\u00f6ckelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir alle wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass lange Erwerbslosigkeit oft auch weitere Probleme wie Suchterkrankungen mit sich bringen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Notwendig sind individuelle Hilfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.400", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne finanzielle Unterst\u00fctzung und passgenaue Beratung kann keine und keiner diese Negativspirale durchbrechen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat auch etwas mit den Rahmenbedingungen in den Jobcentern und deren personeller und finanzieller Ausstattung zu tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier wollen wir zulegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sodass die individuelle Unterst\u00fctzung geleistet und eine hohe Beratungsqualit\u00e4t dauerhaft sichergestellt werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So st\u00e4rken wir die Interessen und Rechte der Arbeitslosen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "angesichts der Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.960", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in den vergangenen Jahren circa 3\u00a0Prozent der ALG-II-Bezieher von Sanktionen betroffen waren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.760", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten wir dieses Thema in unseren Debatten nicht \u00fcberreizen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern lieber konkrete Wege aus der Arbeitslosigkeit finden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.920", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die F\u00f6rderung von Betroffenen muss deutlich mehr Gewicht haben als restriktive Ma\u00dfnahmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.160", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Punkt verweise ich auf das Sondierungspapier von Union und SPD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommt es zur Neuauflage der Gro\u00dfen Koalition, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.440", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird das erfolgreich erprobte Modellprojekt f\u00fcr Langzeitarbeitslose \u201eSoziale Teilhabe am Arbeitsmarkt\u201c in ganz Deutschland angeboten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit bekommen circa 150\u00a0000 Langzeitarbeitslose die Chance auf eine \u00f6ffentlich gef\u00f6rderte Besch\u00e4ftigung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Arbeit zu haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.200", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr sich selbst sorgen zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist eine Frage der W\u00fcrde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit \u00f6ffentlich gef\u00f6rderter Besch\u00e4ftigung geben wir Langzeitarbeitslosen nachhaltige Perspektiven."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.280", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben dem sozialen Arbeitsmarkt geh\u00f6rt die Qualifizierung in den Fokus ger\u00fcckt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hauptursache f\u00fcr Arbeitslosigkeit sind fehlende Schulabschl\u00fcsse und nicht abgeschlossene Berufsausbildungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.200", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Tatsache wird sich noch versch\u00e4rfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.520", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir nicht handeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pr\u00e4ventive Ma\u00dfnahmen im Rahmen der Schulsozialarbeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Jugendberufsagenturen oder der ausbildungsbegleitenden Hilfen sind wichtiger denn je."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank und Gl\u00fcck auf!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege J\u00f6rg Schneider von der AfD-Fraktion h\u00e4lt seine erste Rede. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben das Wort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.960", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege."
   ]
  }
 ]
}